videos.title: Alicia Keys feat. SiR - Three Hour Drive
videos.description: New York City legend @AliciaKeys graces the COLORS stage with an exclusive rendition of ‘Three Hour Drive’ featuring SiR; which is taken from her newly released self-titled album 'Alicia'.

videos.title: Smino - Rice & Gravy
videos.description: St. Louis-born, LA/Chicago-based rapper @smino5058 closes out our collaborative series with @Burberry  with a scorching performance of new single “Rice & Gravy” (produced by fellow COLORS alum @montebooker)

videos.title: SiR - John Redcorn
videos.description: Inglewood’s SiR lays down an emotive performance of ‘John Redcorn’ (produced by Kal Banx & Jeff “Gitty” Gitelman), taken from his latest album ‘Chasing Summer’.

videos.title: Ne-Yo - Don't Love Me
videos.description: South London based singer/songwriter James Vickery treats us to a slick and soulful performance of latest single “Until Morning” (prod. Louis Mattrs) which is lifted from his forthcoming sophomore EP.

videos.title: Eliza - Wasn´t Looking
videos.description: London based singer/songwriter lays down her golden tones which are just as smooth as they are seductive on her stunning performance of new single “Wasn’t Looking”.

videos.title: James Vickery - Until Morning
videos.description: R&B icon @neyo graces the COLORS stage for a special performance as part of our series with Motown Records for Black Music Month.

videos.title: Erick the Architect - Self Made
videos.description: Brooklyn-based producer and rapper @EricktheArchitect222 delivers a razor-sharp performance of his new single ‘Selfmade’.

videos.title: WESTSIDE BOOGIE - STUCK
videos.description: Compton-based rapper @BoogieOfficial  drops by the COLORS stage with a breezy performance of his new single ‘Stuck’ which features his alter egos Anthony and Superblood Boog.

videos.title: SCH - Loup Noir
videos.description: French rapper Julien Schwarzer aka @sch shares a performance of cinematic new song "Loup Noir"

videos.title: Sofiane - Windsor
videos.description: French rapper Sofiane Zermani aka Sofiane (@FiansoOfficiel ) shares a sharp and powerful performance of new single ‘Windsor’.

videos.title: FKJ - Us
videos.description: French multi-instrumentalist and musician @FKJ  (aka French Kiwi Juice) creates a moment of magic with a live performance of ‘Us’, a highlight from his latest album ‘V I N C E N T’.

videos.title: Loyle Carner - HGU
videos.description: South London-based rapper @LoyleCarner eturns to COLORS with an emotional performance of ‘HGU’, the final track of his latest album ‘Hugo’.

videos.title: Brazilian Samba Grooves
videos.description: bom pa caraio

videos.title: Febem - Champions
videos.description: Brazilian rapper @Febemog serves up a powerful performance of his new single ‘Champions’ produced by long-time collaborator CESRV.

videos.title: Knucks - Alpha House/Bando
videos.description: South Kilburn, London-based rapper @Knucks brings his sharp flows to COLORS with a striking medley of his new singles ‘Alpha House’ and ‘Bando’.

videos.title: Unknown T - Goodums
videos.description: Rising British drill artist @unknwnt9 drops by for a fiery performance of new single ‘Goodums’ with pianist Jay Verma

videos.title: Skepta - No Sleep
videos.description: North London’s Skepta is on another level on ‘No Sleep’, a hard-hitting cut taken from his newly released album ‘Ignorance Is Bliss’.

videos.title: Gazo - MOLLY
videos.description: Parisian drill artist Gazo drops by our stage to deliver a powerful performance of his new single ‘MOLLY’.

videos.title: Quasimoto - Jazz Cats Pt. 1
videos.description: Quasimotos's "Rappcats" off that "Further Adventures" album.
